Advert Specifications

File Specification

  • All files transmitted to us should be rendered as a jpg, png or svg format only. All other formats will be rejected
  • Files should be sent to the size of the intended media box(s).
  • Files should not be sent in with a transparent background.
  • Colour RGB only. If a ıle is supplied in CMYK and is featured on the site and appears to have changed colours proptyle waiver the responsibility which is solely the responsibility of you the advertiser or the advertisers agent. Changes will not be possible after publishing.
  • Neither custom transfer functions nor custom halftones are accepted.
  • Image Resolution to be no less than 72dpi.
  • Screen/digital media screen resolution is 72dpi in all instances.

File Preparation

  • Files should have no border..
  • Reverse out white or coloured text should be no smaller than 10pt bold.
  • Reverse out text should not be more than two colours.
  • Fine Serif Type faces should not be used.
  • Body text must be single colour or two colour at most, and no less than 8pt in size.
  • Line weight must not be less than 1pt.
